<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Snow1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Snow,</orth> subst. water congealed into soft white flakes: <bibl n="shak. ven 354" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 354</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ven 354" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 354</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ven 354" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 354</bibl> <bibl n="shak. luc 1218" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1218</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 130.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 130, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.7.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 7, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.106" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 106</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.933" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 933</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.141" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 2, 141</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 4.1.171" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 171</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.59.171" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 59</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.2.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 2, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.191" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 3, 191</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.220" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 220</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.220" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 220</bibl> <bibl n="shak. jn 3.4.176" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 4, 176</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.298" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 298</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 4.260.298" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 260</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.5.50" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 5, 50</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.223" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 223</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.249" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 249</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.326" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 326</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 3.1.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. III, 1, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.2.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 2, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.3.46" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 3, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.35" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 35</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.35" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 35</bibl> <bibl n="shak. lr 2.2.83" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 2, 83</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 2, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 1.4.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 4, 65</bibl>. Emblem of chastity: <cit><quote>the white cold virgin s. upon my heart,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 55</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>chaste as the icicle that's curdied by the frost from purest s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 5.3.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 3, 66</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the consecrated s. that lies on Dian's lap,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.386" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 386</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>as chaste as ice, as pure as s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.1.141" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 1, 141</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>whose face between her forks presages s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.121" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 6, 121</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>as chaste as unsunned s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 2.5.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 5, 13</bibl></cit>. Of hoary age: <cit><quote>sap-consuming winter's drizzled s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 5.312" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 312</bibl></cit>.
